<HEADLINE> After 25 years in prison, freed inmate is retried for 1973 murder  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
    	   ROCHESTER, N.Y. (AP) - Since being freed last spring after 25 years in
prison, John Duval has spent weekdays sweeping the floor and filling in the
appointment book at Val's, his mother's neighborhood beauty salon.
<P>
	   "It's not a job," Duval, 47, said with a shrug during a lunch break at his
