<BODY>
<HEADLINE> AP Corrects Backstreet Birthday  </HEADLINE>
    By The Associated Press
<TEXT>
<P>
	   In a Jan. 12 story listing celebrity birthdays, The Associated Press
erroneously reported that singer A.J. McLean of Backstreet Boys was born on Jan.
19. His birthday is Jan. 9.
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
